    "description": "<p>Established in 2018, Elements Dental is a independent dental clinic, led by an experienced and passionate dental surgeon. We believe that the key to good service begins with its <strong>people</strong> - we want the best for our employees, so that they in turn can give their best to our patients.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Treatments include preventative dentistry, pain management, aesthetic dentistry and orthodontics. We believe in providing treatment tailored to our patient's needs, which means joint decisions between the clinical team and the patients. Our treatments focus on the concepts of <strong>functional aesthetic</strong> and <strong>holistic oral health</strong>.</p>",
